data.title: Necrology
data.text:
“With sore and stricken hearts we mourn…”

In your kindness, please remember the following Fraternity brothers we lost. Notifications received Between June 15, 2022 and

August 9, 2024

Recognize someone special, commemorate a milestone or honor a lost loved one by making a special gift in their name.

If you have a link to a confirmed obituary belonging to a brother we will solemnly include it. We cannot vouch for the contents or effective status of linked obituaries.
